headline.main: 287 MORE SOLDIERS ON WOUNDED ROLL; Sixty-five New Yorkers and 25 Jerseyites Added to North African List CASUALTIES TOTAL 60,164 6,711 Dead, 13,481 Wounded, 25,129 Missing and 14,843 Prisoners, Revised Figures

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, June 1 -- The War Dejartment made public today the names, with next of kin, of 287 United States soldiers wounded in action in North Africa.
abstract: War Dept rept on wounded, N Africa; NY and NJ list
